username":[{"journal_url":"http://tfwalton.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"tfwalton","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"tfwalton","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://tfwalton.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"tfwalton","ctime_ts":1467018344,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?replyto=24700069","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24700069#t24700069","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24700069#t24700069","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24700069#t24700069","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_3722691","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"https://plus.google.com/111183250061977984505","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":24700069,"talkid":96484,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24700069#t24700069","upictitle":"Renan Moreira: pic#0","article":"Good Morning,<br /><br />Dear Martin,<br /><br />First, sorry for my english.<br />My name is Renan, I'm from Porto Alegre/RS Brasil.<br />I know this isnt the place to talk about GOT, but i just want to say Thank you. You are the best writer, the universe that you created is the closest to perfection I've ever read.<br />Thank you, Thank you, for your books, and for bring joy for millions of people around the world.<br /><br />Renan Moreira<br />renansmoreira@outlook.com","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"10 months ago","ctime":"June 27 2016, 13:22:45 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Thank You","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"https://plus.google.com/111183250061977984505","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/google-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"Renan Moreira","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_3722691","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=78135789&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"Renan Moreira","ctime_ts":1467033765,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/124702361/74665646","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?replyto=24700581","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24700581#t24700581","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24700581#t24700581","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24700581#t24700581","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_3051281","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://twitter.com/phimseto","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":24700581,"talkid":96486,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24700581#t24700581","upictitle":"Paul Marzagalli: pic#124702361","article":"George, congratulations to you and Gardner. Your anthologies are always a treat. However, don't be so quick to disregard Old Uranus. Would love to see an anthology of pulpy sci-fi comedies, whether something broad like Mel Brooks might write or something so esoteric in its humor only math professors could chuckle at the jokes within.   ","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"10 months ago","ctime":"June 27 2016, 15:49:18 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Congrats","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://twitter.com/phimseto","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/twitter-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"phimseto","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_3051281","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=74665646&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"phimseto","ctime_ts":1467042558,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/124820222/75122696","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?replyto=24701093","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24701093#t24701093","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24701093#t24701093","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24701093#t24701093","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"langkard","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://langkard.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":24701093,"talkid":96488,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24701093#t24701093","upictitle":"langkard: pic#124820222","article":"Congratulations!  Most definitely a well-deserved award for you and Mr. Dozois. I have thoroughly enjoyed the anthologies edited by the two of you, but Old Mars and Old Venus are by far my favorite anthologies by any editors.  They both succeeded at allowing me to relive the sense of wonder I enjoyed in my youth when I waited impatiently for new editions of Galaxy and If magazines to arrive in the mail. I look forward to more anthologies from the two of you, edited together or individually.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"10 months ago","ctime":"June 27 2016, 19:38:25 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://langkard.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"langkard","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"langkard","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://langkard.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"langkard","ctime_ts":1467056305,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/123371686/70873652","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?replyto=24702373","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24702373#t24702373","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24702373#t24702373","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24702373#t24702373","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_2587046","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=2246029","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":24702373,"talkid":96493,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24702373#t24702373","upictitle":"Frank Probst: pic#123371686","article":"And best wishes to Gardner for a speedy recovery.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"10 months ago","ctime":"June 27 2016, 22:52:12 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Congrats!","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=2246029","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/facebook-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"Frank Probst","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_2587046","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=70873652&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"Frank Probst","ctime_ts":1467067932,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/125501990/73552018","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?replyto=24703653","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24703653#t24703653","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24703653#t24703653","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24703653#t24703653","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"s_scottstephens","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://s-scottstephens.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":24703653,"talkid":96498,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24703653#t24703653","upictitle":"S. Scott Stephens: pic#125501990","article":"Now I'm siting here with a bunch of ideas for an Old Uranus story. I know you're joking but when I read your post I realized how good of a candidate that planet is for a science fiction story. It's just this massive, beautiful,  blue planet with something like 25 or 30 moons orbiting it. The thing is ripe for storytelling to be sure. <br /><br />Sometimes I write full stories with multiple drafts just for fun or practice. I may just write one anyway, in case you and Gardner change your mind. Or hell, I could shop it around anyway if the writing goes well (I'm a fellow gardener).<br /><br />Thanks for the inspiration, George and congrats on your award. I'm really happy for you guys. That was a hell of a book. All those guys deserved it. LOTS of talent going on in those pages. Planet of Fear and the one about the Godstone were top notch. All were pretty good but those two really hit for me. Brilliant stories!","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"10 months ago","ctime":"June 28 2016, 05:24:35 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Well Deserved","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://s-scottstephens.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"s_scottstephens","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"s_scottstephens","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://s-scottstephens.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"s_scottstephens","ctime_ts":1467091475,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?replyto=24706725","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24706725#t24706725","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24706725#t24706725","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24706725#t24706725","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"casejord","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://casejord.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":24706725,"talkid":96510,"etime_ts":"1467218838","thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/491941.html?thread=24706725#t24706725","upictitle":"casejord: pic#0","article":"Hello George, Congratulations!<br /><br />I think this is my first time posting, but thought it would be appropriate to ask about something I've been wondering.<br /><br />Will there be mass-market paperback editions of \"Old Mars\" and \"Old Venus\" in the same way there was one of \"Songs of the Dying Earth\" and the various \"Warriors\" and \"Dangerous Women\" ones?<br /><br />Also, any news about \"The Book of Swords\", Dozois' upcoming solo anthology?<br /><br />Thanks so much.","siteroot":"h